<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport" />
  <title>Magic Link to Career Canvas</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://career-canvas-media.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/93ffa903-70c9-42cc-8100-3d50680b6014"
    rel="icon" type="image/png" />
</head>

<body style="
      align-items: center;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      display: flex;
      font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    ">
  <div style="
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin: auto;
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 20px 60px;
      ">
    <img alt="Career Canvas App Logo"
      src="https://career-canvas-media.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/93ffa903-70c9-42cc-8100-3d50680b6014"
      style="max-height: 100px; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);" />
    <h2 style="
                        font-size: 1.8em;
                        color: #333;
                        margin-bottom: 10px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                    ">
      Welcome to Career Canvas!
    </h2>
    <p style="
                        font-size: 1.2em;
                        color: #555;
                        margin-bottom: 20px;
                    ">
      Click the button below to log in instantly.
    </p>
    <a href="<%= magicLink %>" style="
          background-color: #0052cc;
          border-radius: 5px;
          color: #ffffff;
          display: inline-block;
          font-size: 16px;
          font-weight: bold;
          margin-bottom: 8px;
          margin-top: 8px;
          padding: 12px 24px;
          text-decoration: none;
        ">Login Now</a>
    <p style="
                    font-weight: bold;
                    color: #d9534f;
                    background-color: #f8d7da;
                    border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
                    padding: 10px;
                    border-radius: 5px;
                    margin-top: 20px;
                ">
      Don't share this email with anyone. This is confidential information intended only for you. If you did not
      request this email, please contact our support team immediately at <a href="mailto:support@careercanvas.pro"
        style="color: #d9534f; text-decoration: underline;">support@careercanvas.pro</a>.
    </p>
    <p style="
            color: #888;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding-top: 10px;
        ">
      &copy; 2025 Career Canvas. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>